00:04:55,583 --> 00:04:56,500
[Jean]
Wait for my orders.

47
00:04:56,583 --> 00:04:58,000
[Ferro] Affirmative.

48
00:04:58,083 --> 00:04:59,500
[Jean] Rico, focus on
any shadows you see

