A girl?

60
00:05:26,541 --> 00:05:28,375
Yeah.

61
00:05:30,958 --> 00:05:32,416
I know...

62
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:36,333
it sounds crazy, but, recently
I've been hearing rumors of

63
