Yeah? And I just told you that
you got the wrong room, chief.

85
00:06:51,416 --> 00:06:53,541
You hard of hearing?

86
00:06:53,625 --> 00:06:55,041
No...

87
00:06:55,125 --> 00:06:56,833
Then maybe it's a learning
disorder. Your guy ain't here!

88
00:06:56,916 --> 00:06:58,958
Sorry, I...

89
00:07:02,875 --> 00:07:05,291
Now, get lost before
I pop your eyes out

90
00:07:05,375 --> 00:07:08,541
and make your
sister watch!

91
00:07:12,125 --> 00:07:13,291
[Submachine Baddie] Louie,
what's going on--

92
00:07:31,125 --> 00:07:33,416
Brother...

93
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:38,208
You planning on visiting
every hospital in Italy?

94
00:07:38,291 --> 00:07:40,833
No, uh...
I'm not.

95
00:07:40,916 --> 00:07:43,666
I've already made
my decision.

96
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:45,500
Why does it have
to be children?

97
00:07:45,583 --> 00:07:49,166
These kids have been
through enough already.

98
00:07:49,250 --> 00:07:52,458
It's the agency's call.

99
00:07:52,541 --> 00:07:55,000
The physical alterations,
the brainwashing...

100
00:07:55,083 --> 00:07:57,333
All the conditioning seems
to take much better,

101
00:07:57,416 --> 00:07:59,208
