102
00:08:07,875 --> 00:08:11,083
This is the work of the Social
Welfare Agency, isn't it?

103
00:08:11,166 --> 00:08:12,541
Yes.

104
00:08:12,625 --> 00:08:14,000
[Doctor] Our government's
created quite an impressive

