thought they'd follow through.

107
00:08:19,625 --> 00:08:21,833
Dr. Masi, we
came because...

108
00:08:21,916 --> 00:08:24,000
We have heard that your
facility is housing

109
00:08:24,083 --> 00:08:26,416
a very seriously
injured girl.

110
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:27,875
Yes.

111
00:08:27,958 --> 00:08:30,333
It was tragic... She's in
desperate need of your help.

112
00:08:30,416 --> 00:08:32,125
Last week, her
family was massacred.

113
00:08:32,208 --> 00:08:34,208
But the monsters
kept her alive.

114
00:08:34,291 --> 00:08:35,458
Throughout the night,

115
00:08:35,541 --> 00:08:37,500
