thoughts of suicide.

119
00:09:05,458 --> 00:09:08,041
[Ferro] Have you come up
with a name for her yet?

120
00:09:10,250 --> 00:09:14,166
[Jose]
Henrietta.

121
00:09:14,250 --> 00:09:16,458
Henrietta it is, then.

122
00:09:16,541 --> 00:09:18,500
Thank you.

123
00:09:18,583 --> 00:09:20,083
Once she gets used
to the facility,

124
00:09:20,166 --> 00:09:25,833
we'll move her into
a room with Rico.

125
00:09:25,916 --> 00:09:29,041
She's awake.

126
00:09:48,583 --> 00:09:54,416
[Jose] I see
you're awake.

127
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:56,666
You
thirsty?

128
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:58,375
No,
thanks.

129
00:10:19,666 --> 00:10:22,416
My name
is Jose.

130
00:12:11,791 --> 00:12:14,375
You're up
early.

131
00:12:24,583 --> 00:12:27,916
Did you get
any sleep?

132
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,166
No.

133
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:32,125
Why not?

134
00:12:32,208 --> 00:12:35,083
You told me to get
proficient quickly, Jose.

135
00:12:41,250 --> 00:12:43,375
Stop it.

136
00:12:51,583 --> 00:12:53,208
