You'll never have time
to use it in combat,

138
00:12:55,125 --> 00:12:56,750
so don't get spoiled by it.

139
00:12:56,833 --> 00:12:58,958
Just shoot in the general
direction of the target.

140
00:12:59,041 --> 00:13:00,375
At close range,
it won't matter

141
00:13:00,458 --> 00:13:01,875
what part of their body
you lodge a bullet,

142
00:13:01,958 --> 00:13:03,750
it'll still keep them
from going very far.

143
00:13:31,916 --> 00:13:33,916
Average, Jose.

144
00:14:03,916 --> 00:14:04,833
[Head Baddie]
Hey--

145
00:14:04,916 --> 00:14:06,875
Throw your grenade!

146
00:14:10,458 --> 00:14:13,333
Take him.

147
00:14:29,458 --> 00:14:31,208
[Worker] Good. Now, when you
and your pal there is finished

148
00:14:31,291 --> 00:14:33,791
