has failed.

153
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,500
[Ferro] Roger.
We're on our way.

154
00:15:01,583 --> 00:15:03,166
Yeah.

155
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:20,541
Henrietta, why did
you lose control?

156
00:15:25,208 --> 00:15:26,625
Uh...

157
00:15:26,708 --> 00:15:28,041
This isn't like you...

158
00:15:28,125 --> 00:15:32,083
I've never seen you
lose it like that.

159
00:15:42,125 --> 00:15:45,958
Your arm's been hit.

160
00:15:46,041 --> 00:15:48,958
[Jose] Are you okay?

161
00:15:49,041 --> 00:15:52,416
[Henrietta]
Yes...

162
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:54,208
Jose, we're here.

163
00:15:54,291 --> 00:15:58,333
Ferro. The witness isn't here.
Judging by their reaction,

164
00:15:58,416 --> 00:16:00,500
I'd say he's hiding
in the building somewhere.

165
00:16:00,583 --> 00:16:03,333
I'll put people on it...
Alfonso, Amadeo...

166
00:16:03,416 --> 00:16:05,125
start at the rooftop
and work your way down.

167
00:16:05,208 --> 00:16:08,666
Giorgio, watch the perimeter.

168
00:16:29,125 --> 00:16:30,375
[Jose] Let's go home.

169
