level of conditioning...

172
00:16:46,083 --> 00:16:50,166
You've got to put a bigger
collar on your hunting dog.

173
00:16:50,250 --> 00:16:51,791
I think you're
wrong about that.

174
00:16:51,875 --> 00:16:55,375
Too much conditioning will... 
will shorten her lifespan.

175
00:16:55,458 --> 00:16:59,791
[Jean] Then we just prep a new
patient once she's used up.

176
00:16:59,875 --> 00:17:03,875
You're too emotionally attached
to a tool of the trade.

177
00:17:03,958 --> 00:17:06,291
Jean... enough.

178
00:17:06,375 --> 00:17:08,041
She may have a few issues...

179
00:17:08,125 --> 00:17:10,041
But she's an
excellent assassin...

180
00:17:10,125 --> 00:17:14,416
It would be wasteful to dispose
of Henrietta... Anyway...

181
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:17,666
We got what we came for,
and lost none of our own...

182
00:17:17,750 --> 00:17:21,625
You need to learn to take a
broader perspective of things.

183
00:17:21,708 --> 00:17:24,416
Sir.

184
00:17:30,708 --> 00:17:34,250
Jose... As you know, each
handler is responsible for

185
00:17:34,333 --> 00:17:37,500
