little conditioning, then I'd
like for you to give it a shot.

188
00:17:42,958 --> 00:17:46,375
However, further mistakes
are inexcusable...

189
00:17:46,458 --> 00:17:51,625
Please make certain this is a
lesson she understands.

190
00:17:55,791 --> 00:17:57,708
[Jose]
Yes, sir.

191
00:18:08,916 --> 00:18:10,916
[Jose] Henrietta stayed
as quiet as she could

192
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:13,166
