blame her.

194
00:18:15,250 --> 00:18:17,166
Watching her family
get murdered.

195
00:18:17,250 --> 00:18:19,625
How do you get over
something like that?

196
00:18:19,708 --> 00:18:22,916
How could she wrap her head
around the fact that she,

197
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,916
out of everybody,
