to do something nice?

202
00:18:45,291 --> 00:18:48,333
Or did I choose
her out of pity?

203
00:18:48,416 --> 00:18:51,916
Whatever it was, I knew
I wanted to help her.

204
00:19:28,250 --> 00:19:29,916
[Triela]
Henrietta!

205
00:19:30,666 --> 00:19:32,333
Rico just told me...

206
00:19:32,416 --> 00:19:35,083
