Don't sweat it.

210
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:57,666
Hey -- I know! We can go
have a drink in Claes' room.

211
00:19:57,750 --> 00:19:58,833
A drink?

212
00:19:58,916 --> 00:20:01,041
Yeah. She's got
the best tea,

213
00:20:01,125 --> 00:20:03,916
and I swear she puts
magic in her cakes.

214
00:20:05,791 --> 00:20:10,083
You just wanted to make him
proud of you. That's all.

215
00:20:10,166 --> 00:20:13,666
[Henrietta] Yeah...
I guess so...

216
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:15,750
But Triela...

217
00:20:15,833 --> 00:20:18,000
Isn't that the only
thing any of us can do?

218
00:20:18,083 --> 00:20:21,166
We all seek approval.

219
00:20:21,250 --> 00:20:23,458
And if I were him...

220
00:20:23,541 --> 00:20:27,875
