make me feel uncomfortable.

221
00:20:46,041 --> 00:20:47,125
[Jose] Let's go.

222
00:20:47,208 --> 00:20:48,083
Right.

223
00:21:13,666 --> 00:21:14,791
[Henrietta]
Jose...

224
00:21:18,875 --> 00:21:20,166
Is your arm hurting?

225
00:21:24,708 --> 00:21:26,458
I only...

226
00:21:29,125 --> 00:21:32,333
I just wanted to
help you, Jose.

227
00:21:48,166 --> 00:21:49,791
[Jose] We'll have a
doctor take a look

228
00:21:49,875 --> 00:21:53,208
at that arm as soon
as we get back.

